William Ziegler was jailed in 2001 for the killing of Russell Allen Baker in Mobile . 
  He was initially convicted of capital murder in 2001 but conviction was overturned in 2012 . 
  Judge Sarah Stewart blasted his initial trial and said his lawyers were substandard . 
  He agreed to plead guilty to aiding and abetting murder and walked free today . 
  Comes after Anthony Ray Hinton was freed from death row in April . 
 